Welcome to MYLead!

What is MYLead? As a community, we have a great need for positive and forward thinking leaders.  And as individuals, we have the opportunity to take a leadership role in just about any aspect of life.   The mission of MYLead is to help young leaders realize their potential and build the confidence to transform that potential into positive action.

What do we do at the conference?  We spend a weekend sharing ideas, hearing from community leaders, motivational speakers, and learning about ourselves through personal goal setting and leadership exercises.

Who can attend the conference?  High school sophomores that will be moving into their junior year in 2019

What sets MYLead apart from other conferences? The passion, excitement, and drive that come from this group of people is unbelievable!  Our organization was founded by stupendous leaders over 15 years ago and has impacted the lives of thousands of young leaders ever since. This organization is led 100% by volunteers who are passionate about making a difference in the lives of young leaders.

17th Annual MYLead Conferences
May Conference:  May 17-19, 2019

June Conference:  June 7-9, 2019

www.mylead.org

Students:  Are you interested in attending MYLead and not sure where to begin?  Please email us at recruitment@mylead.org.  Be sure to include: your name, the name of the school you attend, and the city where your school is located.  Let us know you want to attend MYLead and we would be happy to put you in contact with the representative from your school that is in charge of nominations.  (And if you are home schooled, no problem.  Just let us know you are home schooled and we will put you in touch with the correct MYLead representative to facilitate the next steps.)

School Administrators:  Are you ready to change the life of a sophomore from your school?  STUPENDOUS!  We are now accepting nominations for the MYLead Conferences in 2019.  Click on the Login tab above to submit your nomination.  Or, click the MYLead Conference tab above to get more information about our program.  Any questions?  No problem, just send us an email at recruitment@mylead.org and we will have happy to help!
